Halqemeylem\n\nThe prayer \"Blessed is the Spot\"  in Stó:lõ Shxweli Halq'eméylem, the language of the Soowahlie People.\n\nLe plist te shxweli      \n\nQas te lalem             \n\nQas te shxweli           \n\nQas te tówel            \n\nQas te th'ale           \n\nQas te smelmalt         \n\nQas shxwelis eyolemthét \n\nQas te siyótkõwel       \n\nQas te spelhqél         \n\nQas te téméxw           \n\nQas te kw'otl'kwa       \n\nQas te tl'chá:s         \n\nQas te spelhqél         \n\nShxwelis kwes qwelesem te chichelk Siyam shxwelis seys kwes thelhílem","name":"Stolo Shxweli Halqemeylem","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"19598105-bf0f-4b5d-9e66-90f4011c1de5","book_cats":{"be":{"cat":"Блаславёны","cat_order":4,"order_in_cat":1},"bs":{"cat":"Praznik Devetnaest Dana","cat_order":29,"order_in_cat":1},"ca":{"cat":"Qualitats Espirituals","cat_order":30,"order_in_cat":15},"co":{"cat":"Families","cat_order":1,"order_in_cat":1},"cy":{"cat":"Common","cat_order":2,"order_in_cat":1},"de":{"cat":"Allgemein","cat_order":1,"order_in_cat":1},"en":{"cat":"Gatherings","cat_order":23,"order_in_cat":1},"et":{"cat":"Katsumused ja raskused","cat_order":8,"order_in_cat":5},"fa":{"cat":"طلب مدد و حمایت","cat_order":20,"order_in_cat":1},"fa-translit":{"cat":"طلب مدد و حمایت","cat_order":20,"order_in_cat":1},"fr":{"cat":"Familles","cat_order":9,"order_in_cat":1},"fy":{"cat":"Tafelgebedens","cat_order":15,"order_in_cat":1},"haw":{"cat":"General Prayers","order_in_cat":2},"ht":{"cat":"Lwanj ak Rekonesans","cat_order":26,"order_in_cat":5},"hu":{"cat":"Család","cat_order":7,"order_in_cat":2},"is":{"cat":"Lofgjörð og þökk","cat_order":21,"order_in_cat":1},"kl":{"cat":"Katerisimaarnerit","cat_order":19,"order_in_cat":1},"km":{"cat":"General Prayers","order_in_cat":1},"lg":{"cat":"OKUBEERWA","cat_order":17,"order_in_cat":2},"lt":{"cat":"Vaikai","cat_order":12,"order_in_cat":1},"ml":{"cat":"ഐക്യം","cat_order":8,"order_in_cat":2},"pap":{"cat":"Gatherings","cat_order":3,"order_in_cat":1},"ro":{